Business Brief -- Spar Aerospace Ltd.:
   Aerospace Company Plans
   MacDonald, Dettwiler Bid
Spar said closely held MacDonald has about 11 million
shares outstanding, a large proportion of which are held by
employees. It said the largest holder, Ventures West, a
venture-capital concern in Vancouver, British Columbia, plans
to tender the 23% of MacDonald it controls.
   Spar has about 11.5 million shares outstanding. In trading
on the Toronto Stock Exchange Friday, Spar shares closed at
C$18.25, down 37.5 Canadian cents.